name: Shipyards Night Market
description:
Shipyards Night Market 2.0
 
 
 
 We would like to thank everyone for attending this year. We are now planning for 2024, stay tuned for exciting announcements.
 
 This long running event is now under a new management team dedicated to delivering a fun evening for all ages.
 
 Our weekly Friday market at North Vancouver's Shipyard District features live bands, dj's, food trucks and artisan craft vendors.
 
 Hours: 3pm and until 10pm.
 
 
 
 Come down and enjoy great music, food and drinks in one of the lower mainlands best outdoor venues. The southern view overlooking downtown Vancouver is unbelievable, take a walk along the waterfront and the Burrard Dry Dock Pier.
 
 
 
 Don't forget to support the local businesses in the area too.

name: Fresh St. Market - Vancouver House
description:
Fresh St. Market is a place to shop, to explore, to discover and more than that - it is a community-gathering place.
 
 
 
 Fresh St. Market offers top-of-the-line products in an atmosphere of discovery and exploration where new, authentic, local, organic and exclusively sourced becomes everyday shopping.
 
 
 
 Come and explore at Fresh St. Market. Discover and try out what's amazing and delicious in a place where everyone's invited in on great fresh foods. Where Fresh Meets Every Day.
 
 
 
 We're proudly B.C. family owned and absolutely thrilled to be bringing a unique food shopping experience to Vancouver House and the Beach District.
